INFO

Untar and put the ampache directory into $HOME/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins
or /usr/lib/rhythmbox/plugins

Run rhythmbox (preferable with "-D ampache" from command line)

Open Edit -> Plugins dialo box, enable " Ampache Library"

Click Configure, enter your infromation, for example URL:
	http://test.com/server/xml.server.xml

Clock on Ampache under Library, songs should appear in the browser
(possibly with a large delay as it synchronosly downloads the data)

Seva <seva@sevatech.com>

